Package: dust
Type: Package
Title: Optimal partitioning algorithm for univarite data using duality simple tests (dust)
Version: 0.2.0
Author: c(person("Simon", "Quern√©", email = "simon.querne@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")), person("Vincent", "Runge", email = "vincent.runge@univ-evry.fr", role = c("aut", "cre")), person("Charles", "Truong", email = "ctruong@ens-paris-saclay.fr", role = c("aut")))
Maintainer: Vincent Runge <vincent.runge@univ-evry.fr>
Description: Algorithms for detecting multiple changes within time-series. The detection is based on the minimization of a penalized likelihood. We use a dynamic programming algorithm called optimal partitioning with a new pruning method (dust): DUality Simple Test.
